00:43:17.761 --> 00:43:20.898
Hmm.
Are you cancer free?

541
00:43:21.865 --> 00:43:23.800
Very good.

542
00:43:23.833 --> 00:43:25.902
"As far as we know."

543
00:43:25.935 --> 00:43:28.238
I knew what
she meant.

544
00:43:28.271 --> 00:43:30.841
So from now on.
no more talk from you.

