00:47:13.329 --> 00:47:15.365
I'm glad
I came over to talk.

616
00:47:15.398 --> 00:47:17.367
Yeah.
Lovely to meet you.
Joan.

617
00:47:22.372 --> 00:47:24.174
I take it
that's him then?

